{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>How will you survive when the world begins to fall apart?</strong><br>Welcome to <i>Emergent-Z</i>\u2014the ultimate pre-apocalyptic zombie survival experience, where every decision shapes your story. Fight to survive as a human or embrace chaos as a zombie. The choice is yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Fight for Survival as a Human</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Scavenge for supplies and fortify your base to withstand the growing undead threat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Team up with survivors, assign tasks, and keep everyone alive.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every mistake is deadly\u2014zombies are always hunting.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Lead the Horde as a Zombie</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Command a relentless horde and unleash chaos on human survivors.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Grow stronger with every victim and unlock unique zombie abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Outwit fortified defenses in the ultimate battle for dominance.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Live the Outbreak</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dynamic day-night cycles, resource management, and the freedom to shape your story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>EmergentSync</i> connects every player\u2019s world in a shared, evolving apocalypse.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The outbreak is here\u2014humanity\u2019s survival hangs by a thread. Will you rise to the challenge or plunge the world into chaos? Choose your side in <i>Emergent-Z</i>!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271250/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738624186","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2271250/page.bg.jpg?t=1738624186","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamsta